
To run the container in daemon mode do the following:

currently setup to crawl every six hours

docker run --name usncrawler -v /root/usncrawler/usnrepo:/opt/usncrawler/usnrepo -d usncrawler \
    --elastic-search http://demo3.sl.cloud9.ibm.com:9200 --repo-dir /opt/usncrawler/usnrepo --sleeptime 21600

For single host deployment in demo3 the elastic search url is:

demo3.sl.cloud9.ibm.com
The repodir is /root/usncrawler/usnrepo

For cloudsight distributed deployment:
elastic search url is elastic2-cs.sl.cloud9.ibm.com

repordir is /root/usncrawler/usnrepo
